    <item>
      <title>Training of the mind</title>
      <link>/wiaposts/training-of-the-mind/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Jun 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/wiaposts/training-of-the-mind/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/wiapost/5161-Training-Of-The-Mind.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Training of the mind&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Training of the mind 
    &lt;div id=&#34;training-of-the-mind&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#training-of-the-mind&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since the first of our life  &lt;br&gt;
All parts and systems of our body are designed,  &lt;br&gt;
developed, trained, used, and maintained  &lt;br&gt;
in such a way that survival of the life is kept  &lt;br&gt;
at the helm of everything, we do or create.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mother nature teaches that to us. &lt;br&gt;
Our parents and friends teach us this. &lt;br&gt;
Our teachers and instructors teach  &lt;br&gt;
that to us in the classroom and playground.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
